Combine water, grape juice, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, and KOOL-AID(R) Soft Drink Mix in a pitcher, stirring until SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener dissolves. Pour 3/4 cup of the mixture into each of 8 tall glasses; add 1/4 cup of the seltzer to each glass. Top each serving with 1/4 cup of the ice cream. Serve immediately. Store leftover prepared drink in refrigerator.